public class ObservableModel
extends Observable

The ObservableModel class is an extension of Observable, which provides a minimal implementation of the Observer pattern in Java. In addition, the ObservableModel class also provides an internal Property class, which allows for the notification of property changes to subscribed Observers.

See Also:
Observable, Observer, ObservableModel.Property
